Third Department,

July, 1973

(July 2, 1973) In the Matter of Jack B. Weinstein, Appellant, v. John P. Lomenzo, as Secretary of State of the State of New York, et al., Respondents.—

Judgment, Supreme Court, Albany County, entered on June 28, 1973, affirmed, without costs. No opinion, Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals granted, without costs. Herlihy, P. J., Staley, Jr., Cooke, Sweeney and Kane, JJ., concur.
